arStrings.szText: Pek de keyif verici (hıçkırık) bir iş değil sanki, ha?
Knowingly teasing; the work they're doing is a bit morbid. (The "(hic)" is a dunken hiccup.)
Sen de benim kadar fazla insan yakana kadar bekle... Tanıdığın insanların neredeyse hepsini...
Regular volume for the first half, in a mock-joking/proud tone. Then a bit quieter and more somber, in the second half. He's trying to cover up his pain and isn't totally succeeding.
